  Penetration testing
  white hat-hired to help companies
  black hat-hacks to steal something
  grey hat-hack with good intentions but may break a law or two
  Social Engineering-manupulating people for information--How Stanley hacked the banked
  Personally Identifiable Information PII-phone number, address, social secruity number, email, and passport
  Don't click pop-ups
  If the email address doesn't match content, delete it.
  Whenever it involves banking, call phone number on back of credit card to check.
  Keep antivirus software up to date
